rows.label: tlk46400071_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh dear.
This is a bind...

rows.label: tlk46400071_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Thing is, there's a wreck been
washed into the harbor.

rows.label: tlk46400071_04_msg0003
rows.name:
And it's pretty big. Well, if the truth
be told, it's massive!

rows.label: tlk46400071_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Not sure whether the lads can handle
it by themselves...

rows.label: tlk46400071_04_msg0005
rows.name:
But it needs getting rid of somehow,
so I'm on the lookout for some
specialist help.

rows.label: tlk46400071_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Whoever takes it on will need to be
super strong, and there's just no one
like that round here...

rows.label: tlk46400071_04_msg0007
rows.name:
Can't really ask the refugees for help
either, so I really am in a bind.

rows.label: tlk46400071_04_msg0009
rows.name:
Oh, you'd help!
Thank you, that's be most appreciated.

rows.label: tlk46400071_04_msg0010
rows.name:
I'm looking forward to seeing what
you can do!
